## Title of workshop
Hedgehog Bot

## Skill Level
Beginner-Intermediate

## Duration of workshop
2 hours

## Workshop Details
Build a two wheeled robot that you can control from your phone

## Preparation and Equipment
Bring a laptop with the Arduino software installed, please install the ESP8266 Board package, instructions on how to do this are available at http://hedgehogbot.digimakers.co.uk/setup.html if you have trouble please come a bit earlier to the workshop so we can help you setup your machine.

## Number of participants
15

## How many times can you deliver the workshop throughout the day?
2

## What are your technical requirements or location requests? 
Quiet room is ideal.

## Do you need extra helpers to deliver the workshop, if so how many?
3 (total of 4 people running workshop)
